Package de.hu.gralog.beans.propertydescriptor Description

This package defines all PropertyDescriptors that are currently available in GrALoG.

PropertyDescriptors are used to define PropertyEditors for properties of algorithms, structures, vertices and edges in GrALoG. You can define your own PropertyDescriptor by either subclassing one of these or by directly subclassing PropertyDescriptor. Note that you also have to define a corresponding PropertyEditor.
